modules.description: Handles operations like mesh triangulation, node and element manipulation, and geometry export. Works with triangular mesh data structures, including nodes, edges, and faces. Supports exporting meshes to LaTeX, SciLab, and Matlab for visualization and analysis.

Provides functions to create and manipulate planar straight-line graphs, including adding vertices, edges, and constraints. Works with geometric data types such as points, line segments, and polygonal boundaries. Used to generate meshes for computational geometry tasks like finite element analysis or terrain modeling.
